################################################################################
###########                FTI INSTALLATION FILE                  ##############
################################################################################


======================>   COMPILE AND INSTALL FTI   <======================

 * There are no dependencies, you just need GCC and MPI.

 * You have to set variables in the Makefile before compiling:
    - FTIPATH : Path to the directory where you want to install FTI
    - MPIPATH : Path to your MPI directory

 * make

 * make install

 * make clean   (if you want to clean your local directory)


======================>   UNINSTALL   <======================


 * make uninstall


